@startuml
|User|
start
: (1) Click on Import good button in\nInventory Management screen;
|System|
: (2) Display Import good form;
|User|
repeat: (3) Select Product;
: (4) Enter quantity;
repeat while(More product?) is (yes) not (no)
: (5) Click Confirm button;
|System|
: (6) Save import information to database;
: (7) Send notification to inventory manager;
: (8) Generate warehouse receipt;
: (9) Display warehouse receipt;
|User|
if(Choose export warehouse receipt?) then (Yes)
  |System|
  : (10) Export warehouse receipt;
else (No)
end if
stop
@enduml
